  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6 and boil a full kettle</p><p>Peel and finely slice the <strong>brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Heat a large wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-low heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onions</strong> with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and cook for 10-12 min or until really softened</p>",
